Basic steps:
- Give the following commands:
    - activate myEnv
    - django-admin startproject <project_name>
    - python manage.py startapp <app_name>
- add <app_name> in INSTALLED_APPS in project_name/settings.py
- add urls.py in the <app_name> folder
- add the templates folder and the corresponding path in the TEMPLATES[0].dir field
- add the static folder and the static folder path below static folder urls in settings.py
- to load static files in html, add {% load static %} after first row
- add path('<name_app>/', include('<name_app>.urls')) to project_name/urls.py
- add the urls you want in the <app_name>/urls.py
- write some request -> ... functions in the views.py folder



